<h2>Report Update</h2>

<p>Hello <%= @report.user.email %>,</p>

<p>We've reviewed your report submission and unfortunately, it cannot be processed at this time.</p>

<div class="info-box">
  <h3 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1e40af;"><%= @report.title %></h3>
  <p><strong>Location:</strong> <%= @report.address %></p>
  <p><strong>Barangay:</strong> <%= @report.barangay.name %></p>
  <p><strong>Category:</strong> <%= @report.category.name %></p>
  <p><strong>Priority:</strong> <%= @report.priority.titleize %></p>
  <p><strong>Status:</strong> <span class="status-badge status-closed">Closed</span></p>
  <p><strong>Submitted:</strong> <%= @report.created_at.strftime("%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p") %></p>
  
  <p><strong>Description:</strong></p>
  <p style="background-color: white; padding: 15px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;"><%= @report.description %></p>
</div>

<div style="background-color: #fef2f2; padding: 20px; border-radius: 6px; border-left: 4px solid #ef4444; margin: 30px 0;">
  <h4 style="margin-top: 0; color: #dc2626;">Possible reasons for rejection:</h4>
  <ul style="margin: 0;">
    <li><strong>Duplicate report:</strong> Similar issue already reported in the same area</li>
    <li><strong>Insufficient information:</strong> Description or location details unclear</li>
    <li><strong>Inappropriate content:</strong> Report contains inappropriate language or content</li>
    <li><strong>Outside jurisdiction:</strong> Issue is not within barangay responsibility</li>
    <li><strong>Spam detection:</strong> Report flagged for suspicious patterns</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<div style="background-color: #dbeafe; padding: 20px; border-radius: 6px; border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6; margin: 30px 0;">
  <h4 style="margin-top: 0; color: #1e40af;">What you can do:</h4>
  <ul style="margin: 0;">
    <li><strong>Submit a new report:</strong> With more detailed information</li>
    <li><strong>Contact us directly:</strong> If you believe this was an error</li>
    <li><strong>Check existing reports:</strong> See if your issue was already reported</li>
    <li><strong>Provide more details:</strong> Include photos, exact location, etc.</li>
  </ul>
</div>

<%= link_to "Submit New Report", url_for(controller: 'reports', action: 'new', only_path: false), class: "button" %>

<p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 14px; color: #64748b;">
  <strong>Report ID:</strong> #<%= @report.id %><br>
  <strong>Thank you for your understanding and continued support!</strong>
</p>
